<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/668863-anyone-can-tell-at-last-who-is-the-one">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[anyone can tell At last,who is the one that Yukiho loves the most. i am so confused now. As detective Imaeda said,Yukiho loves Shinozuka Kazunari. But Is it possible that the man she loves is Ryoji. I can't help thinking about this issue. And another question is Who is the one that told Enomoto about the place that Natsumi -secretary for Ryoji's company stayed. Is he Ryoji???? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_668863'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F19256975-journey-under-the-midnight-sun">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/668863-anyone-can-tell-at-last-who-is-the-one">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/668863-anyone-can-tell-at-last-who-is-the-one">See all 3 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/40142491-alex-perez"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1423593403i/40142491._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/40142491-alex-perez">Alex Perez</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Imaeda&apos;s belief that Yukiho liked Kazunari was just his theory, because he had no idea about who Ryo was. He just had &quot;one side&quot; of the story. It isn&apos;<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Imaeda's belief that Yukiho liked Kazunari was just his theory, because he had no idea about who Ryo was. He just had "one side" of the story. It isn't explicitly stated (ever), but it is assumed the only person she trusts in the world is Ryo (and vice versa). <br />For your second question, I think you mean Namie (and not Natsumi), the "accountant" for the gaming company. It has to be Ryo that sold her out. He was the only one who knew he would be there at the Nagoya hotel.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
